<p style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #1f2937; margin: 0 0 8px 0;">
  새로운 견적 문의가 접수되었습니다
</p>
<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #6b7280; margin: 0 0 28px 0; line-height: 1.6;">
  관리자님, <strong style="color: #1f2937;"><%= @quote.contact_name %></strong>님으로부터 견적 문의가 도착했습니다.
</p>

<div style="background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-left: 4px solid #00a859; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 28px;">
  <!-- 문의자 정보 -->
  <p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #00a859; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">문의자 정보</p>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; width: 100px;">이름</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 600;"><%= @quote.contact_name %></td>
    </tr>
    <% if @quote.company_name.present? %>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">회사명</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 600;"><%= @quote.company_name %></td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">이메일</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937;"><%= @quote.email %></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">연락처</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937;"><%= @quote.phone %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- 프로젝트 정보 -->
  <p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #00a859; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">프로젝트 정보</p>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; width: 100px;">유형</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 600;"><%= @quote.project_type %></td>
    </tr>
    <% if @quote.budget.present? %>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">예산</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937; font-weight: 600;"><%= @quote.budget %></td>
    </tr>
    <% end %>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">접수 시간</td>
      <td style="padding: 6px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #1f2937;"><%= @quote.created_at.strftime("%Y년 %m월 %d일 %H:%M") %></td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- 상세 내용 -->
  <p style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: #00a859; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin: 0 0 12px 0;">상세 내용</p>
  <div style="background: white; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= @quote.message %></p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA 버튼 -->
<div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px;">
  <a href="<%= ENV.fetch('APP_URL', 'https://designd.co.kr') %>/admin/quotes/<%= @quote.id %>"
     style="display: inline-block; padding: 14px 36px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00a859, #00d670); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">
    관리자 페이지에서 확인하기
  </a>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center; margin: 0;">
  이 메일은 D.us 웹사이트에서 자동으로 발송되었습니다.
</p>
